==English==
===Etymology===
From {{F.}}, from {{L.}} perfect passive participle ''[[transpositus]]'', from ''[[transponere]]'', to put across, from ''[[trans]]'', across, and ''[[ponere]]'', to put

===Pronunciation===
*Verb:
**[[AHD]]: trănzpōz' ''or'' tränzpōz' (''UK'')
**[[IPA]]: /trænzˈpəʊz/ ''or'' /trɑːnzˈpəʊz/ (''UK'')
**[[SAMPA]]: /<tt>tr{nz"p@Uz</tt>/ ''or'' /<tt>trA:nz"p@Uz</tt>/ (''UK'')
**{{audio|en-us-transpose-verb.ogg|Audio (US)}}
